+**Architecture:** Add a small resolver component that owns Apollo switches, pool whitelist validation, and fallback selection. Keep old behavior behind the default-off optimize switch, and only change lock timing when the optimized path is enabled. Existing item-level locks and task skip switches stay in the base classes.
